# Bookings API & data

Read **`docs/agents/bookings.md`** before non-trivial changes.

- Storage: SQLite `data/bookings.db` via `lib/bookings-store.ts`; business logic in `lib/db.ts`. Legacy `bookings.json` auto-imported once if DB empty.
- All routes under `app/api/bookings/` require `requireApiSession()` from `lib/require-session.ts`.
- `bookedBy` / `bookedByEmail` come from the session on create/update — never trust the client body.
- Conflict check: same date + room (`className`) + overlapping HH:mm times.
- List endpoint: filtered GET returns `{ bookings, total, page, limit, totalPages }`; query parsing in `lib/booking-query.ts`.
- Availability: `GET /api/bookings/availability` — busy rooms include optional `conflict` summary for the panel UI.
- Bulk range: `POST /api/bookings/bulk` — one record per day, shared `seriesId`; HTTP 207 on partial success.
- Rooms: `lib/rooms.ts` (`ROOM_OPTIONS`) is the canonical room list.

When adding query params or response fields, update `docs/agents/bookings.md` and **`AGENTS.md`**.
